org.openimaj.demos

Annotation Type DemoPackage


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=PACKAGE)
public @interface DemoPackage
    An annotation for annotating packages that contain demos. This provides a means for categorizing demos by placing them in annotated packages.

    The annotation itself is set within the package-info.java

    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String description
      A description of the demo.
      String[] keywords
      Keywords associated with the demo.
      String title
      The display name of the demo package.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String icon
      The resource URI of an icon to represent the demo [optional]

    • Element Detail

      • title

        public abstract String title
        The display name of the demo package. No more than 30 characters

      • description

        public abstract String description
        A description of the demo. As long as you like.

      • keywords

        public abstract String[] keywords
        Keywords associated with the demo.

      • icon

        public abstract String icon
        The resource URI of an icon to represent the demo [optional]
        Default:
        "/defaults/demo.png"
